Mutant Vehicles

Notorious P.I.G.
Someone needed to bring a pig to wallow in the mud. After six months, 60 hours and a nearly exploded garage later, Burning Man bore witness to the ultimate road hog—the Notorious P.I.G. Blood, sweat and tear’d from scratch, this hog-hog was the product of pure and simple curiosity. Over the course of six months, I taught myself welding, bovine electrical therapy, hairstyling, motorcycle mechanics and problem-solving on a grand scale. 
The making of Nortorious P.I.G.
